originalText.text: I left my car here for 2 nights when we returned to pick up the car the Airpods that I had left in the back seat were missing. I called them back to report it and they completely denied taking it. We knew for fact that someone had been in the back seat because whoever was there dropped a coupon in the back seat that wasnt there before. Not to metion that they're over priced. Would NOT recommend.

originalText.text: Absolutely terrible. I wish I could give this 0 stars. When we went to pick up our car, in the snow and rain after an msg show, and they were a disorganized mess. They had blocked in the cars who parked their early with other cars and had no idea where the keys to these more recently parked were. It was like they were hoping for people to show up perfectly in the reverse order they arrived. They had no dedicated lane for cars to leave. They were still letting new and monthly cars in the lot while dealing with this. Totally unprepared for an msg show. My 8 months pregnant wife and I had to wait in the show and rain for 45 minutes with the 20 other people that this lot held up. This was a disaster.
